{
  "screen_id": "obs-register-done",
  "route": "/observe/register/done",
  "title": "保存しました",
  "layout": "standard",
  "notes": "V3-AIP-101 観測登録スライス1(F6)。保存直後のΔrecap+次の目安のゼロタップ登録(POST /observation/schedule)。この画面では間隔30日固定(stage:'unspecified')で登録する簡略版 — 個体の現ステージに応じた間隔自動選択は今後の波(ponytail: stage_interval のスキーマ採番後にテンプレ側へ)。register_schedule opt-out時は自動登録せず、ボタンは手動登録として残る(死んだボタンにしない)。params.id はここでは capture_id(useRunAction の queryFromResult が API 応答の capture_id/individual_id を常に `id` に載せる規約のため)。個体参照は F2 が hidden field で運んだ params.individual_id を使う。",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "shell",
      "type": "app-shell",
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "page",
          "type": "page",
          "children": [
            { "id": "title", "type": "heading", "props": { "text": "保存しました", "level": 1 } },
            {
              "id": "individual",
              "type": "card",
              "props": { "source_path": "/api/v1/individuals/{{params.individual_id}}" },
              "children": [
                {
                  "id": "recap-weight",
                  "type": "text",
                  "props": {
                    "text": "体重 {{params.weight_g}}g",
                    "compare_source": "individual",
                    "compare_item": "weight",
                    "compare_unit": "g",
                    "compare_current": "{{params.weight_g}}",
                    "compare_exclude": "{{params.id}}"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "recap-length",
                  "type": "text",
                  "props": {
                    "text": "体長 {{params.length_mm}}mm",
                    "compare_source": "individual",
                    "compare_item": "length",
                    "compare_unit": "mm",
                    "compare_current": "{{params.length_mm}}",
                    "compare_exclude": "{{params.id}}"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "schedule-register",
              "type": "button",
              "props": {
                "label": "次の目安を登録",
                "auto": true,
                "auto_when": "{{params.register_schedule}}",
                "success_label": "✓ 次の目安 登録済み — {{date}} 頃(間隔30日)",
                "success_label_date_from": "result.next_observation_at",
                "static": {
                  "individual_id": "{{params.individual_id}}",
                  "stage": "unspecified",
                  "from": "{{now}}",
                  "template.stage_interval_days.unspecified": 30
                }
              },
              "action": { "kind": "api", "method": "POST", "path": "/api/v1/observation/schedule" }
            },
            {
              "id": "add-more",
              "type": "button",
              "props": { "label": "同じコに追加", "variant": "primary" },
              "action": { "kind": "navigate", "to": "obs-register-entry?id={{params.individual_id}}" }
            },
            {
              "id": "done",
              "type": "button",
              "props": { "label": "完了", "variant": "secondary" },
              "action": { "kind": "navigate", "to": "home" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "transitions": []
}
